OPEN POSITION
WestRock Company (NYSE: WRK) partners with our customers to provide differentiated paper and packaging solutions that help them win in the marketplace. WestRock’s 50,000 team members support customers around the world from more than 300 operating and business locations spanning North America, South America, Europe and Asia. Learn more at www.westrock.com.
Open Position: Process Engineer – Pulp Mill
Job Location: Fernandina Beach, FL
The Opportunity:

The Fernandina Beach Mill is a fully integrated facility producing high quality linerboard for the packaging industry.
How you will impact WestRock:
Utilize your technical expertise to improve the efficiency and cost of operations by working in collaboration with Production and Maintenance departments
Assist Operating departments by applying engineering methodologies to problem solving
Work with hourly and salaried employees to improve mill business results
Become valued member of operating and/or maintenance team and learn supervisory skills

What you need to succeed:

Bachelor’s degree in Chemical Engineering or Pulp & Paper Science
Must have the desire, drive and excellent work ethic to progress into operations management positions
Strong interpersonal and leadership skills are essential
Must have well developed written communication skills
Excellent planning, organizational, time management and prioritization skills
Proficient computer skills (including MS Office)
Must be eligible to work in the United States

What we offer:

Corporate culture based on integrity, respect, accountability and excellence
Comprehensive training with numerous learning and development opportunities
An excellent compensation package commensurate with the skills, competencies and potential of the candidate
A career with a global packaging company where Sustainability, Safety and Inclusion are business drivers and foundational elements of the daily work.

WestRock Company is an Equal Opportunity Employer committed to creating and maintaining a diverse workforce: Minorities/Females/ Disabled/Veterans.
